Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.02,0:00:12.55,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Hiya, everyone! I’m Osawa Rurino!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.03,0:00:15.78,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rurino-chan!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:17.41,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Looks like we’re in the same class!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.45,0:00:29.37,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,So wait, that means that she visited our club room before she’d officially transferred in…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.47,0:00:32.03,Kaho,,0,0,0,,She must’ve been really motivated!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.37,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You know what to do, right, Sayaka-chan?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:44.15,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Huh? What? Why do you look so serious?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:50.73,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Rurino-chan belongs to the School Idol Club, okay?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.29,0:00:53.36,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,So… what?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.31,0:00:58.76,Kaho,,0,0,0,,That means… that no matter what, we can’t let her get stolen away by any other club…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:03.74,Kaho,,0,0,0,,She’s a very, {\i1}very{\i0} important new member of ours…!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:07.06,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Hmhm, it’ll be okay.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.45,0:01:11.31,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,She was so enthusiastic about joining the club, after all.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.81,0:01:13.71,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I’m sure she’s already made up her mind.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:18.29,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Volleyball?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.65,0:01:22.90,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ooh, actually, that might be pretty fun, too!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:24.57,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Basketball?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.88,0:01:26.85,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Not bad, not bad at all!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:29.91,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m pretty good at ball games, you know~?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:35.67,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Kaho-san!? Why is she getting tempted so easily!?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.71,0:01:38.36,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Listen, Sayaka-chan…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:45.60,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Not everyone in the world fully commits to things like you…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.11,0:01:50.96,Kaho,,0,0,0,,In fact, there’s a ton of people that can’t say no to an invitation!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:52.06,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Like me!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:54.54,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Oh, no…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:58.45,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,What should we do…?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:02.15,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Desperate times call for desperate measures…!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.82,0:02:05.36,NPC,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Osawa-san!\N{\fs40}[Ena]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.61,0:02:07.13,NPC,,0,0,0,,Wanna try out for the school choir~?\N{\fs40}[Ena]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:12.40,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Choir? It’d feel good to sing really loudly, huh~!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:15.24,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Hold it!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:19.27,NPC,,0,0,0,,Ah–! W-where’d you come from!?\N{\fs40}[Ena]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:21.29,NPC,,0,0,0,,Why are you butting in, Kaho-chan!?\N{\fs40}[Ena]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:26.46,Kaho,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! You arrived pretty recently, right, Rurino-chan!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.03,0:02:31.28,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan and I were planning on showing you around the place!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:34.93,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Oh, that’d be really nice!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:42.16,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Let’s go, Rurino-chan! C’mon, hurry!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:50.39,NPC,,0,0,0,,Ah–! Hey!! We were just about to recruit a new club member–!\N{\fs40}[Ena]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:54.79,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Seems like everyone had the same idea, huh…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.29,0:03:04.80,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Phew… thanks for that~.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:10.79,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Hasunosora’s such a big school, I actually had trouble finding the club room yesterday…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:14.29,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Nah, it’s no problem!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:22.27,Rurino,,0,0,0,,If I didn’t find it, I was just gonna give up and find another club to join.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.27,0:03:25.12,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ahaha, that was a close one~.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:29.76,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Since we’re on lunch break, I’m gonna show you every nook and cranny of this school!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.09,0:03:32.39,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You’ll know everything like the back of your hand!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:33.91,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Woo~!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:41.10,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Let’s start here!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:44.89,Kaho,,0,0,0,,This is the School Idol Club’s room!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:47.47,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay!{\i0} Gotcha!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:56.70,Kaho,,0,0,0,,This is the school otter!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:04:00.56,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Everyone likes feeding it, so it’s nice and chubby.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:05.47,Rurino,,0,0,0,,So kyute! Can I pet it!?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:13.60,Kaho,,0,0,0,,And this is the warehouse…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:19.22,Kaho,,0,0,0,,The club stores lots of older things in it, but…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:23.54,Kaho,,0,0,0,,It’s really easy to get lost, so make sure you’re always with someone in here, okay!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:27.22,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Huh~ What is this place?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:30.48,Rurino,,0,0,0,,It’s like a haunted house~! Seems exciting!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:33.66,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Ah, Rurino-chan!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.40,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You shouldn’t go any deeper in here!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:38.50,Kaho,,0,0,0,,We need to be back before lunch ends, you know!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:46.63,Kaho,,0,0,0,,A-And this is… gasp!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:52.24,Kaho,,0,0,0,,We ran into the School Idol Club room again!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:59.16,Kaho,,0,0,0,,It’s the coolest, most fun, and the most amazing place in all of Hasunosora!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:02.71,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Kaho-san, you’re being extremely obvious!\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:04.71,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ahaha!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:19.20,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Anyway, even though we’ve been to a bunch of places, there’s a lot of really important history to this school.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:21.98,Rurino,,0,0,0,,History, huh…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:25.05,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I don’t really get that stuff.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:28.05,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’d rather have sugary than history, anyway…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:30.84,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Cogito, ergo Ruri.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:32.59,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Uh…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:35.76,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I-I’m kinda the same way too, I think!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:43.23,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ve noticed how good the convenience store sweets are since I came back to the country…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:45.96,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You’re so right!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:47.94,Kaho,,0,0,0,,But those things have so many calories!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:50.53,Rurino,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about!?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:53.36,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You know how bad the calories would get in America!?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:58.02,Rurino,,0,0,0,,My morning run went from being a hobby to a necessity!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:05:59.78,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Huh!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:05.40,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,…It feels like they have a lot in common.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:09.45,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Like, they both get so animated sometimes…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:12.61,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Did you say something, Sayaka-chan?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:14.88,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing important.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:19.68,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking how it’s like you’ve known each other for a long time.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:24.38,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Ehehe, Rurino-chan’s just really easy to talk to!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:26.66,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Yeah, same here!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.66,0:06:28.59,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Looks like it worked then!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:33.46,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I knew it’d be worth it to work hard to show up in Kaho-chan’s dreams every night~!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:36.14,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Wait, are you haunting me!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:39.91,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You two really have gotten quite close, hehe.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:47.48,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, yes! I’m fine, thank you! Best friend! Yaaay!{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:50.73,Kaho,,0,0,0,,W-Whoa! Did you hear that, Sayaka-chan!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:54.78,Kaho,,0,0,0,,That was actual English! She must’ve learned so much overseas!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:59.84,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I’m pretty sure I could understand more than I should have…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:02.80,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Wow!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:05.76,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Keep saying stuff, Rurino-chan! Anything!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:07.98,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Hehe~!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:10.32,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay, okay!{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:14.14,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a pen!{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:17.23,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I’m school idol! {\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:20.29,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Very, very nice girl!{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:22.63,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Woo! Yeah!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:26.57,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…Guh–…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:28.81,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Rurino-san?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:33.63,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait… a… little…{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:37.27,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I’m… uh…{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:42.07,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ah, I think my battery is already out…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:45.97,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:48.34,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Battery?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:53.73,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Sorry! I’ve got something I gotta do over in the second-year classrooms!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:56.13,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You guys just go back, ‘kay? {\i1}Goodbye!{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:00.55,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,…There she goes.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:03.51,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I wonder what got into her…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:05.91,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Ah!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.02,Kaho,,0,0,0,,…No way!!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:09.57,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:14.77,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Is she trying to sneak around and check out the other clubs while we’re not looking!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:15.98,Kaho,,0,0,0,,We’ve gotta follow her!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:19.00,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,But, Kaho-san…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:24.56,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Even if that were the case, she {\i1}is{\i0} free to choose what clubs she wishes to join…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:29.32,Kaho,,0,0,0,,But, Sayaka-chan…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:31.70,Kaho,,0,0,0,,We finally found a new club member…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:36.61,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Even if you give me those puppy dog eyes, we shouldn’t do things we shouldn’t.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:39.18,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You’re not Tsuzuri-senpai…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:47.05,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I mean, of course I want her to join the School Idol Club, but even so…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:52.51,Kaho,,0,0,0,,…Okay, I understand, Sayaka-chan.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:09:00.23,Kaho,,0,0,0,,So we shouldn’t interfere, but we {\i1}do{\i0} have to show just how much more charming the School Idol Club is than all the other clubs!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:01.79,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:03.97,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:08.10,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Sure, that sounds about right!\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
